tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE legislation_changes (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    law_number INT,
    law_description VARCHAR,
    change_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE legislation_versions (
    version_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    legislation_id INT,
    version_description TEXT,
    version_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (legislation_id) REFERENCES legislation_changes(id)
);
